      "title": "API Design & Architecture",
      "subtitle": "Build APIs that other developers actually want to use",
      "weeks": "4-5 weeks",
      "description": "Go beyond REST — learn GraphQL with Apollo Server, tRPC, gRPC, OpenAPI documentation, and software design patterns that make codebases maintainable at scale.",
      "modules": [
        {
          "id": "5.1",
          "title": "REST Best Practices",
          "lessons": [
